stream
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 778 Tm (- Athens is typed as City) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 761 Tm (- City is a subclass of Place) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 744 Tm (- Aristotle teaches Philosophy) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 721 Tm (This dataset is only a demo target for the thesis repository. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 706 Tm (implementation itself is not hardcoded only for these six triples.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 673 Tm (Basis Encoding) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 644 Tm (For basis encoding, each triple \(s, p, o\) is converted into a computational) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 629 Tm (basis state:) Tj ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 64 604 Tm (subject_bits || predicate_bits || object_bits) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 582 Tm (Important details:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 557 Tm (- subject and object share the same ID space) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 540 Tm (- predicates use a separate ID space) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 523 Tm (- bit widths are computed dynamically from the loaded graph) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 506 Tm (- the displayed bitstring is kept explicit so the Qiskit endianness is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 491 Tm (  easier to interpret) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 468 Tm (The framework can also build a small uniform superposition over the encoded) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 453 Tm (triple states for demonstration purposes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 420 Tm (Amplitude Encoding) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 391 Tm (Amplitude encoding is defined over triple indices:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 366 Tm (- `|i>` corresponds to the `i`-th triple in the current graph context) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 349 Tm (- the vector is padded automatically to the next power of two) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 332 Tm (- the state is normalized automatically) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 309 Tm (If no custom weights are provided, the project uses a default strategy such as) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 294 Tm (uniform weights.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 269 Tm (For the running example, the experiment script uses the thesis demo vector:) Tj ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 64 244 Tm ([2, 1, 3, 1, 1, 2]) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 222 Tm (which is padded automatically to length 8 before state preparation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 189 Tm (Phase Encoding) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 160 Tm (Phase encoding is also defined over triple indices.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 135 Tm (The pipeline:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 110 Tm (1. creates a uniform superposition over the valid triple indices) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 91 Tm (2. applies a phase shift to marked states) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 72 Tm (3. applies a Hadamard mixing step to create interference) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
