BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 768 Tm (The marking rule is reusable. It is not hardcoded only for Aristotle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 743 Tm (Examples:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 68 718 Tm (- mark triples by predicate URI) Tj ET
